column1: Source: USDA Branded Food Products Database Release July 2018 Software v.3.9.5 2018-08-15
Nutrient data for: CADBURY MARVELLOUS CREATIONS CHOCOLATE ROCKY ROAD, UNPREPARED, GTIN: 07622210464538
Food Group:  Branded Food Products Database

Ingredients: MILK**, sugar, cocoa butter, fructose-glucose syrup, vegetable fats (palm, shea), cocoa mass, WHEAT flour, emulsifiers (E442, E476, sunflower lecithin), humectant (glycerol), strawberry puree, WHEAT fibre, invert sugar syrup, tapioca and maize starch, gelling agent (pectin), acidity regulators (citric acid, malic acid, E452), dextrose, vegetable oils (rapeseed, sunflower), thickener (E407), raising agents (sodium bicarbonate, ammonium bicarbonate), salt, hydrolysed vegetable protein, flavourings, pumpkin concentrate, blackcurrant concentrate, colour (beetroot red), beetroot juice. **The equivalent of 426ml of fresh liquid milk in every 227g of milk chocolate.MILK CHOCOLATE: MILK SOLIDS 20% MINIMUM, ACTUAL 23%.COCOA SOLIDS 20% MINIMUM.CONTAINS VEGETABLE FATS IN ADDITION TO COCOA BUTTER..  MAY CONTAIN NUTS, EGG, SOYA. Date available: 11/10/2017 Date last updated by company: 12/08/2016
